These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
City: new-york, berlin, prague, hamburg, london, nizza, paris
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, volleyball, climbing, handball, weightlifting, snowboarding
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 2. the person who's sport is handball is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 3. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 5. the person traveling to prague is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to london is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
11. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| City           | london | hamburg | berlin | prague | new-york | nizza | paris |
| Sport   | ice-hockey    | handball   | climbing      | weightlifting | volleyball    | skateboarding    | snowboarding         |

