.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, bus, train, bike, motorbike, jet-ski, tram
There are 7 different nationalities: american, australian, spanish, mexican, argentine, nigerian, canadian
 1. the argentine is the person driving the bike##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the canadian##1
 3. the nigerian is on the far right##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the australian##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the mexican##1
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 7. the argentine is in the middle##1
 8. the argentine is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the train##1
10. the person driving the bike is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Transport          | boat | bus | motorbike | bike | jet-ski | tram | train |
| Nationality   | australian      | spanish   | mexican   | argentine      | american       | canadian       | nigerian     |

