.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: ivory, azure, emerald, brown, chestnut, blood-red, amber
There are 7 different nationalities: malaysian, brazilian, argentine, french, mexican, colombian, thai
 1. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 2. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the thai##1
 3. the brazilian is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 4. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 5. the malaysian is the person who likes chestnut##1
 6. the argentine is on the right of the brazilian##1
 7. the brazilian is on the left of the argentine##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the french##1
 9. the person who likes blood-red is the french##1
10. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the malaysian##1
11. the french is in the middle##1
12. the person who likes amber is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Color   | azure | chestnut     | emerald  | blood-red       | ivory       | amber  | brown   |
| Nationality    | colombian  | malaysian | thai | french | brazilian | argentine | mexican |

