.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, van, jet-ski, snowmobile, ship, roller, quad-bike
There 7 different types of food: mango, banana, zucchini, eggplant, papaya, pineapple, strawberry
 1. the person driving the ship is the person eating banana##1
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 4. the person eating mango is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 6. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is the person eating papaya##1
10. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person driving the van##1
11. the person eating strawberry is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Transport   | roller    | quad-bike     | snowmobile     | jet-ski      | van | ship      | scooter     |
| Food   | eggplant | zucchini | pineapple | papaya | strawberry | banana | mango |

