.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
There are 7 different nationalities: french, japanese, malaysian, chinese, canadian, polish, nigerian
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, alhambra, chaman, fonseca, blend, bluemaster, bolivar
 1. the japanese is the bolivar-smoker##1
 2. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the canadian##1
 3. the bluemaster-smoker is in the middle##1
 4. the blend-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 5. the blend-smoker is the polish##1
 6. the canadian is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 7. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the nigerian##1
 8. the malaysian is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the chinese is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
10. the canadian is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Nationality   | japanese | malaysian | polish     | chinese | nigerian | canadian | french |
| Cigar     | bolivar   | chaman    | blend | bluemaster     | tiparillo         | fonseca     | alhambra        |

