.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
7 different pets are kept: ferret, chinchilla, rabbit, turtle, bird, rat, goat
The people have 7 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, hiking, magic-tricks, camping, baking, board-games
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is in the middle##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
10. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Pet    | rabbit | rat   | ferret | turtle | goat  | bird | chinchilla |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks   | camping | fishing | baking     | gardening | board-games | hiking   |

