 3. the person drinking soy-milk is the police-officer##1
 4. the electrician is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the chef##1
 6. the freelancer is on the left of the chef##1
 7. the journalist is the person drinking cola##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
 9. the freelancer is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the journalist is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | soy-milk | lemonade | iced-tea | tea     | water | cola |
| Job     | paramedic | police-officer      | freelancer | chef    | electrician | engineer   | journalist  |

