 4. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 6. the craftsman house is the person watching spy movies##1
 7. the art-deco house is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 9. the art-deco house is in the middle##1
10. the craftsman house is on the right of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
