 4. the person playing bridge is in the middle##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is the person traveling to new-york##1
 6. the person playing monopoly is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
10. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
11. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

