 5. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 7. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
10. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5      |     6      |    7     |
| Beverage   | coffee    | tea    | soy-milk   | 7up | milk | mirinda | fanta   |
