 5. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 7. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 8. the person drinking cola is the person who growsaconite##1
 9. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
10. the person who growsorchid is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
| Flower         | zinnia | aconite   | amaryllis | orchid | tulip | marigold | begonia  |
